== 申请流程 ==
填写申请和平队需要长达一个小时除非与招募人员谈话，申请人必须年满18岁并且是美国公民，并且在他们想离开时间的9至12个月之前申请。他们必须通过面试。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.peacecorps.gov/apply/ |title=One must be 18 years old and a U.S. Citizen to apply |last= |first= |date= |website=Peacecorps |access-date=8 October 2016 |archive-date=2020-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222182317/https://www.peacecorps.gov/apply/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

